body: - Changed sample data set URL

## Bugs Fixed
- Crashing of Pipeline
App moved to a separate Developer Account **Mobile Genomics** in Google Play

## New Features
- Add nCoV-2019 novel coronavirus bioinformatics protocol (Artic_C)
- Add Consensus Generation pipeline (Bcftools)
- Add Variant Calling pipeline (Nanopolish)

## Bugs Fixed
- Add f5c-meth-freq to Demo Mode
- Fix app crash when settings write permission not given

## New Features
- Add option to load previous configuration for standalone mode
- minIt dateset download & unzip automated
- App settings implemented
- Add flag to keep screen on while running the pipeline
- Add option to dim the display when a pipeline is running

## New Features
- Add f5c methylation freq option
- Show a timer when running a tool
- Add tool versions to help screen

## Changed
- Update minimap2 library[armeabi-v7a]

-  Update minimap2 library

## Changed
- Update call methylation args

- Now you can redo a crashed job
- Add option to choose files to be uploaded

## New Features
- Now you can connect to [f5n-server](https://github.com/AnjanaSenanayake/f5n_server) to get a job

## Bugs Fixed
- Show error message when crashed due to out of memory

## New Features
- Show Samtools peak RAM
